subtitle: the single most important message today
stay strong know that that which cannot
kill you makes you
stronger because we have resources that
are deeper than anyone could ever
imagine yes when things are going on a
superficial level we don't always know
our inner strengths but when we're
challenged you suddenly see the unity
look at the unity in Israel look at the
unity around the world the
vigils the the Gathering of people
together in unity in
prayer that is what we must do stay
strong because the strength that comes
from your mind and your heart and soul
is what gives us the strength to be able
to fight any battle look at someone God
forbidden in a hospital when they have
friends they have prayers they have
people supporting them it strengthens
your immunity system so stay strong both
in Israel and abroad and we will prevail
